  <name>Linux AI Assistant</name>
  <summary>AI-powered assistant for Linux terminal commands</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Linux AI Assistant helps you generate, understand, and execute Linux commands using natural language. It leverages Google Gemini to interpret your requests and provide relevant command-line instructions and explanations.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Natural language to command conversion</li>
      <li>AI-powered explanations for commands</li>
      <li>Direct execution of commands (with safety checks)</li>
      <li>Support for dark and light themes</li>
      <li>Command history</li>
      <li>Offline support with cached explanations</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
